comments.raw_text:
The relevant code in widget/src/cocoa/nsLookAndFeel.mm is:

98     case eColor_TextSelectBackground:
99       aColor = GetColorFromNSColor([NSColor selectedTextBackgroundColor]);
100       break;
101     case eColor_highlight: // CSS2 color
102       aColor = GetColorFromNSColor([NSColor alternateSelectedControlColor]);
103       break;

Josh, the fact that "highlight" and "TextSelectBackground" return different things dates back to bug 371053.  And there seems to be no CSS color mapping to TextSelectBackground....

